---
title: "Art Gallery"
layout: gallery-index.njk
desc: "Lorem Ipsum blah blah blah"
eleventyNavigation:
  key: Gallery
  parent: Art
pagination:
  data: artGallery
  size: 12
  reverse: true
  alias: previewimage
permalink: "{% if pagination.pageNumber == 0 %}/art/gallery/index.html{% endif %}{% if pagination.pageNumber > 0 %}/art/gallery/{{ pagination.pageNumber + 1 }}.html{% endif %}"
---

<h1>Gallery</h1>
<p>Click on an image to see its description. Shorter descriptions are in the alt text.</p>
